For cooker:
potato, carrot, peas, tomato. Leave for boiling (4 whistles).

For tadka:
Onion, capsicum, salted butter. 

Start with oil and cumin seed. Add onion and chili. Two spoons of ginger garlic, add (1 full green capsicum). 1.5 chili powder, 1 spoon
coriander power, 2/5 turmeric, lot of pav bhaji masala. Then fry nicely. After removing water, smash and then mix with tadka. Add water. Can
add pav bhaji masala on top. 
